<a name="sub6759225_1" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="创作背景" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">paradise</span>创作背景</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="1" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:250px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/paradise/7081073/0/ac6eddc451da81cb5d0ddbb35a66d016082431e0?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="标题图片" style="width:250px;height:80px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/-4o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D250/sign=f854bc16c4bf6c81f3372bed8c3fb1d7/ac6eddc451da81cb5d0ddbb35a66d016082431e0.jpg"  alt="标题图片" style="width:250px;height:80px;"/>
</a>
<span class="description">
标题图片
</span>
</div><a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%85%B7%E7%8E%A9%E4%B9%90%E9%98%9F">酷玩乐队</a>的主唱<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%85%8B%E9%87%8C%E6%96%AF%C2%B7%E9%A9%AC%E6%B1%80">克里斯·马汀</a>从<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%B8%83%E9%B2%81%E6%96%AF%C2%B7%E6%96%AF%E6%99%AE%E6%9E%97%E6%96%AF%E6%B1%80">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀</a>和<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%B2%8D%E5%8B%83%C2%B7%E8%BF%AA%E4%BC%A6">鲍勃·迪伦</a>的作品中找到了创作灵感。除此之外，歌曲的灵感还来源于<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%85%8B%E9%87%8C%E6%96%AF%C2%B7%E9%A9%AC%E6%B1%80">克里斯·马汀</a>女儿爱波·马汀。<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%85%8B%E9%87%8C%E6%96%AF%C2%B7%E9%A9%AC%E6%B1%80">克里斯·马汀</a>表示《<a target=_blank href="/item/Paradise/7081073" data-lemmaid="7081073">Paradise</a>》是单曲《<a target=_blank href="/item/Every%20Teardrop%20Is%20a%20Waterfall">Every Teardrop Is a Waterfall</a>》的续集，而且《<a target=_blank href="/item/Paradise/7081073" data-lemmaid="7081073">Paradise</a>》的歌词中有一句就是“Every Teardrop Is a Waterfall”。专辑《<a target=_blank href="/item/Mylo%20Xyloto">Mylo Xyloto</a>》的创作过程中，乐队成员演奏了许多乐器以后，《<a target=_blank href="/item/Paradise/7081073" data-lemmaid="7081073">Paradise</a>》浮现在了他们的脑海，最初乐队成员准备用不插电音乐的形式来制作这首歌，后来发现不可能<sup>[6]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[6]_6759225">&nbsp;</a>
。</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="2" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub6759225_2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="歌曲歌词" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
