<div class="para" label-module="para">but it flew away from her reach</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">so she ran away in her sleep</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">and dreamed of para- para- paradise,</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">para- para- paradise, para- para- paradise</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">every time she closed her eyes</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">when she was just a girl</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">she expected the world</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">but it flew away from her reach</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">and the bullets catch in her teeth</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">life goes on, it gets so heavy</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">the wheel breaks the butterfly</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">every tear a waterfall</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">in the night, the stormy night,</div>
