<div class="para" label-module="para">in the night, the stormy night,</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">away she&#39;d fly</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">and dreams of para- para- paradise</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">para- para- paradise</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">para- para- paradise</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">oh oh oh oh oh oh-oh-oh-oh</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">she&#39;d dream of para- para- paradise</div>
