<div class="para" label-module="para">para- para- paradise</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">oh oh oh oh oh oh-oh-oh-oh</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">lalalalalalalalalalala</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">and so lying underneath those stormy skies</div>
