<div class="para" label-module="para">this could be para- para- paradise</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">could be para- para- paradise</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">could be para- para- paradise</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">oh oh oh oh oh oh-oh-oh-oh<sup>[7]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[7]_6759225">&nbsp;</a>
</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="2_2" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub6759225_2_2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="中文" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="2-2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">paradise</span>中文</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">当她还只是个小女孩的时候</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">她对世界充满希冀和期待</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">但这世界背离了她的愿望</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">于是 她逃离世界，进入了她的梦境</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">她梦见了天堂</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">（重复）</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">每一次她闭上眼睛的时候。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">当她还只是个小女孩的时候</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">她对世界充满希冀和期待</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">但这世界背离了她的愿望</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">子弹穿过了她的牙齿</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">生命在继续，可变得越来越沉重</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">滚滚的车轮碾碎了美丽的蝴蝶</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">每一滴泪水都化作瀑布</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">在一个风雨交加的晚上</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">她将会闭上眼睛</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">她梦见了天堂（重复）</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">她梦见了天堂</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">她躺在狂风暴雨的天空下</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">她会说：哦，我知道</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">明天朝阳跃出地平线的时候</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">天堂就会来临</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">必定会是天堂</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">（重复）<sup>[8]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[8]_6759225">&nbsp;</a>
</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="3" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub6759225_3" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="歌曲鉴赏" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">paradise</span>歌曲鉴赏</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="3" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">当小提琴的声音进入耳朵，鼓点从无到有，主唱那略带慵懒的声音开始吟唱，一个神秘的宗教故事也就开始了<sup>[9]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[9]_6759225">&nbsp;</a>
。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">《<a target=_blank href="/item/Paradise/7081073" data-lemmaid="7081073">Paradise</a>》如同一尊华丽的号角，吹响美丽的瞬间。首先是大气的器乐开场，然后简单的钢琴伴奏以及克里斯·马汀真切的歌声在主歌部分相随而行。大量繁华的字符铺垫着副歌，渲染其磅礴的气势。歌曲的副歌部分很容易映入听众的脑海。歌词不只是描写一个女人的梦想，而是在描写一个更精彩的世界<sup>[10]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[10]_6759225">&nbsp;</a>
。歌曲沸腾的音符串联、剑拔弩张的合成器、重低音的节拍给听众带来了一场盛宴<sup>[11]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[11]_6759225">&nbsp;</a>
。</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="4" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub6759225_4" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="歌曲MV" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">paradise</span>歌曲MV</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="4" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/paradise/7081073/0/d788d43f8794a4c2ae27245506f41bd5ad6e394c?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:118px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/-Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=182abf1a0123dd542573a06ae109b3df/d788d43f8794a4c2ae27245506f41bd5ad6e394c.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:118px;"/>
</a>
</div>歌曲的MV由<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%A9%AC%E7%89%B9%C2%B7%E6%80%80%E7%89%B9%E5%85%8B%E9%B2%81%E6%96%AF">马特·怀特克鲁斯</a>执导，MV的结尾部分摄于<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%8D%97%E9%9D%9E/127666" data-lemmaid="127666">南非</a>动物自然保护区，MV中演唱会的场景来自MX巡演的南非<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%BA%A6%E7%BF%B0%E5%86%85%E6%96%AF%E5%A0%A1">约翰内斯堡</a>，于2011年10月19日被发布。MV开头，<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%85%8B%E9%87%8C%E6%96%AF%C2%B7%E9%A9%AC%E6%B1%80">克里斯·马汀</a>扮成大象，从伦敦的天堂野生动物园中逃跑。最开始，他骑自行车来到地铁站，并从坐地铁来到飞机场。随后，他偷偷进入飞机，并把自己装在一个旅行箱中。下机后，他靠街头卖艺挣钱，最终买到了一辆独轮车。骑着独轮车，他来到了动物自然保护区，见到扮成大象的乐队成员们<sup>[12]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[12]_6759225">&nbsp;</a>
。</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="5" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub6759225_5" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
